de.susebox.jtopas.impl

Class SequenceStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.susebox.jtopas.impl.SequenceStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeywordHandler, SequenceHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NoCaseSequenceStore

    public class SequenceStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements SequenceHandler, KeywordHandler
    This class is used by StandardTokenizerProperties to store and search special sequences, comments and strings as well as keywords. The class is not suitable for standalone use since it does not check parameters for null values, assumes a thread-safe context etc.
    Author:
    Heiko Blau
    See Also:
    StandardTokenizerProperties, SequenceHandler
